static Parfactor StdParfactor.getInstance()
          Deprecated. Returns a constant parfactor, the neutral factor for multiplications. Any parfactor multiplied by the constant parfactor does not change.

The constant parfactor contains only one value, 1. There are no parameterized random variables or constraints in this parfactor.
